OL,3,CPolice pledge to tackle shoplifters
OL,4,Cand phone thieves despite huge cuts
OL,6,FLondon police chiefs are promising to
OL,7,Ftarget shoplifters and phone thieves
OL,8,Fin a huge cost-cutting reorganisation
OL,9,Faimed at saving #260m.
OL,11,FScotland Yard plans to transfer 170
OL,12,Fofficers to neighbourhood teams in
OL,13,Fseven of London's worst crime hotspots.
OL,15,FThe Met was forced to shrink its
OL,16,Fheadcount by 1,700 before March 2026
OL,17,Fafter failing to secure enough
OL,18,Fadditional funding from the government
OL,19,Fand the mayor.
