OL,3,CPolice pledge to tackle shoplifters
OL,4,Cand phone thieves despite huge cuts
OL,6,FThe fresh focus on crime hotspots will
OL,7,Fsee officers move to the West End,
OL,8,FBrixton, Kingston, Ealing, Finsbury
OL,9,FPark, Southwark and Spitalfields.
OL,11,FBut the change in emphasis will see
OL,12,Fthe abolition of the Royal Parks
OL,13,FPolice, the removal of police officers
OL,14,Ffrom schools and cuts to the mounted
OL,15,Fsection, dog units, traffic officers
OL,16,Fand the flying squad.
OL,18,FThe force is also drawing up plans to
OL,19,Fclose front counters at some police
OL,20,Fstations and cut opening hours at
OL,21,Fothers.
