OL,6,FSenior officers have called the
OL,7,Freorganisation "Tough Choices".
OL,9,FThe Met insisted it was "ruthlessly
OL,10,Fprioritising" its resources on core
OL,11,Fpolicing and putting more officers on
OL,12,Fthe beat.
OL,14,FThe changes will see up to 80 officers
OL,15,Fmoved to the West End to tackle
OL,16,Fantisocial behaviour, violence against
OL,17,Fwomen and girls, shoplifting and phone
OL,18,Ftheft.
