OL,3,CPolice pledge to tackle shoplifters
OL,4,Cand phone thieves despite huge cuts
OL,6,FThe move comes 24 hours after the
OL,7,FPolicy Exchange think tank reported a
OL,8,F60% jump in muggings involving knives
OL,9,Fin central London.
OL,11,FAnother 90 police will be deployed in
OL,12,Fthe six other "town centres"
OL,13,Fidentified as having the most thefts
OL,14,Fand robberies.
OL,16,FMet Commissioner Sir Mark Rowley said:
OL,17,F"The Met is getting smaller but more
OL,18,Fcapable."
