OL,6,FHe added: " We have a laser-like focus
OL,7,Fon ensuring our officers and staff are
OL,8,Fin roles where they can drive down
OL,9,Fcrime on issues that matter the most
OL,10,Fto Londoners."
OL,12,FLondon mayor Sir Sadiq Khan said the
OL,13,Fnew initiative was bolstered by an
OL,14,Fadditional #32m from the Home Office
OL,15,Fand City Hall.
